description.en:
Mynt is a digital cryptocurrency that is designed to be ASIC resistant. Mynt utilizes the Groestl algorithm for Proof-Of-Work. The Groestl algorithm has one of the lowest power consumption, heat, and noise when compared with other algorithms. 

MYNT is dedicated to being ASIC resistant and will fork if any ASICs are proven to be in existence. These qualities help make Mynt a currency that the average user can use and support with their own hardware.

With no premine, no ico and no unfair mining , Mynt is a fair coin for everyone.
